{"tid":488962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"免費啪啪啪！？ 台灣ptgf 價目表曝光😻","createTime":"2017-12-04T08:14:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T12:21:59.000Z","uid":38886,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e16af5b4b703256d97402d28f2dad199f0ce21a6","tid":488962,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T08:14:15.000Z","msg":"12月是個令人容易感傷的月份，尤其聖誕夜、跨年夜只有一個人過的時候。<br />\n有網友在臉書社團爆廢公社「出租自己」，特別針對聖誕、跨年有需求的網友，且男女不拘。<br />\n洋洋灑灑的價目表，以小時為計費單位，舉凡摸頭、捏臉、陪看月亮、冒充對象、背黑鍋等，收費從100元至1萬元。<br />\n甚至還有「啪啪免費」的促銷，但有錢不一定買得到，因對象由原PO自選。<br />\n網友覺得新奇，紛紛詢價；也有人抱怨太貴了，租一晚下來很不划算。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/04/161358_ded0a0824405fc72a422701cb95f7bf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F04%2F161358_ded0a0824405fc72a422701cb95f7bf3.jpg&h=f1b72c0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85c1ca411ef3426aa6505ae94551d2e5af85380f","tid":488962,"uid":60123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T08:21:00.000Z","msg":"陪看月亮 陰天半價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa82801da07a00bf0a0614584962d1640b6af356","tid":488962,"uid":76216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T08:41:38.000Z","msg":"用(羊)做單位又點台灣?"},{"pid":"1431c5ce706b780d0b5af23ca0c07e3d67fa3d34","tid":488962,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T08:43:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用(羊)做單位又點台灣?</blockquote><br />\n日本貨，仲抵deal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4def8385d3f2886305a3b3e73a3b246bdc5b295b","tid":488962,"uid":38886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T09:23:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用(羊)做單位又點台灣?</blockquote><br />\n補返來源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： <a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171204/1253069/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft